<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:08:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国和尼泊尔登山者在西藏希夏邦马峰遭遇雪崩身亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-nepalese-climbers-killed-by-avalanche-on-shishapangma-in-tibet/articleshow/104254032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104254032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;西藏希夏邦马峰发生雪崩，造成一名美国和尼泊尔登山者死亡，另有两人失踪。希夏邦马峰是世界第 14 高山峰，被认为是同等高度中较容易攀爬的山峰之一。雪崩的规模及其对该地区其他登山者的影响仍不清楚。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 05:26:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-nepalese-climbers-killed-by-avalanche-on-shishapangma-in-tibet/articleshow/104254032.cms</guid></item><item><title>真主党袭击沙巴农场后，以色列袭击黎巴嫩</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-strikes-lebanon-after-hezbollah-hits-shebaa-farms/articleshow/104255086.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104255086.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列向黎巴嫩南部发动炮击，以回应真主党针对以色列军事阵地的袭击。目前还没有人员伤亡的报告。此前，巴勒斯坦枪手对以色列城镇发动突然袭击，造成多人死亡。真主党声称对这次袭击负责，并表示这是为了声援巴勒斯坦人民。以色列军方还对真主党哨所进行了无人机袭击。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 05:53:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-strikes-lebanon-after-hezbollah-hits-shebaa-farms/articleshow/104255086.cms</guid></item><item><title>真主党轰炸与叙利亚戈兰高地接壤的争议地区的以色列阵地</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-bombards-israeli-positions-in-disputed-area-along-border-with-syrias-golan-heights/articleshow/104254868.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104254868.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 05:44:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-bombards-israeli-positions-in-disputed-area-along-border-with-syrias-golan-heights/articleshow/104254868.cms</guid></item><item><title>真主党声称火箭弹和大炮袭击了以色列占领的沙巴阿农场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-claims-rocket-artillery-attack-on-israeli-occupied-shebaa-farms/articleshow/104254250.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104254250.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 05:30:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-claims-rocket-artillery-attack-on-israeli-occupied-shebaa-farms/articleshow/104254250.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗地震造成的死亡人数上升至“1000多人”：政府</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/death-toll-from-afghanistan-earthquakes-rises-to-more-than-1000-government/articleshow/104253432.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104253432.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;政府发言人表示，阿富汗西部偏远地区周日发生的一系列地震造成的死亡人数急剧上升至“1000多人”。周六赫拉特省发生里氏6.3级地震，随后发生了一系列强烈余震，“不幸的是，伤亡人数实际上非常高……死亡人数已超过千人”。 sjd-jts/福克斯/aha</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 05:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/death-toll-from-afghanistan-earthquakes-rises-to-more-than-1000-government/articleshow/104253432.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国和法国加强犹太场所的安全</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-france-step-up-security-at-jewish-sites/articleshow/104253069.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104253069.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯对以色列发动突然袭击后，德国和法国周六采取行动，加强犹太寺庙、学校和纪念碑周围的安全。法国将重点放在全国各地城市的犹太寺庙和学校上，一位犹太领导人对冲突可能蔓延到那里的可能性表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 04:36:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-france-step-up-security-at-jewish-sites/articleshow/104253069.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院议员斯卡利斯和乔丹目前陷入双向议长竞赛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-houses-scalise-jordan-locked-in-two-way-speaker-race-for-now/articleshow/104253113.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104253113.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;凯文·麦卡锡(Kevin McCarthy)下台后，史蒂夫·斯卡利斯(Steve Scalise)和吉姆·乔丹(Jim Jordan)正在争夺美国众议院领袖席位，但选举结果尚不确定。斯卡利斯筹集了资金并在党内建立了关系，而乔丹是右翼煽动者和唐纳德·特朗普的主要捍卫者。特朗普支持乔丹，但尚不清楚这会产生多大影响。到目前为止，两位候选人都获得了大约二十打的支持。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 04:39:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-houses-scalise-jordan-locked-in-two-way-speaker-race-for-now/articleshow/104253113.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴伐利亚州黑森州的选民认为肖尔茨的联盟将受到中期打击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/voters-in-hesse-bavaria-seen-dealing-mid-term-blow-to-scholzs-coalition/articleshow/104252722.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104252722.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国反对派保守派预计将在黑森州和巴伐利亚州选举中获胜，这对总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨的中左翼联盟造成打击。对移民、绿色转型成本和经济停滞的担忧给这些运动蒙上了阴影。极右翼的德国另类选择党（AfD）也有望获得支持。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 04:17:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/voters-in-hesse-bavaria-seen-dealing-mid-term-blow-to-scholzs-coalition/articleshow/104252722.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗地震后救援人员彻夜工作</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/afghan-rescuers-work-through-the-night-after-deadly-quake/articleshow/104252054.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104252054.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿富汗西部一场地震将房屋夷为平地，绝望的救援人员彻夜搜寻幸存者，随着灾难的严重程度逐渐明朗，预计周日死亡人数将上升至 120 人。国家灾害管理局发言人表示，他们预计死亡人数“将会上升非常高”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 03:37:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/afghan-rescuers-work-through-the-night-after-deadly-quake/articleshow/104252054.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚总理对原住民权利公投获胜的希望渺茫持乐观态度</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australia-pm-optimistic-of-long-shot-win-in-indigenous-rights-referendum/articleshow/104251456.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104251456.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管民意调查落后，澳大利亚总理安东尼·艾博内塞对公投能否成功承认土著人民纳入该国宪法表示乐观。这次公投被称为“议会之声”，旨在将原住民纳入宪法，并建立一个咨询机构，听取他们对政策的意见。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 03:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australia-pm-optimistic-of-long-shot-win-in-indigenous-rights-referendum/articleshow/104251456.cms</guid></item><item><title>散居海外的犹太人哀悼以色列遭受的袭击，但仍继续庆祝节日</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/jewish-diaspora-mourns-attack-on-israel-but-carries-on-by-celebrating-holidays/articleshow/104251308.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104251308.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;住棚节假期结束后和庆祝《托拉》期间发生的哈马斯袭击使散居海外的犹太人遭受重创。世界各地的犹太教堂举行了庄严的仪式，信徒们祈祷治愈和解决问题。犹太节日期间发生的袭击事件并非巧合，因为历史上以色列就是在这些时期成为攻击目标的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 03:01:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/jewish-diaspora-mourns-attack-on-israel-but-carries-on-by-celebrating-holidays/articleshow/104251308.cms</guid></item><item><title>厄瓜多尔候选人谋杀案第七名嫌疑人在监狱中死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/seventh-suspect-in-ecuador-candidate-murder-dies-in-prison/articleshow/104251219.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104251219.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;七名被指控暗杀厄瓜多尔总统候选人费尔南多·比亚维森西奥的哥伦比亚囚犯在监狱中死亡。死亡事件发生在两起不同的事件中，六名囚犯在瓜亚基尔的一所监狱中被杀，一名囚犯在基多的印加监狱中被杀。这些囚犯与比亚维森西奥的谋杀案有关，比亚维森西奥以反腐败努力而闻名。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 02:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/seventh-suspect-in-ecuador-candidate-murder-dies-in-prison/articleshow/104251219.cms</guid></item><item><title>尽管国会大力支持，但 60 亿美元的乌克兰援助如何在政府拨款法案中崩溃</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/how-6-billion-in-ukraine-aid-collapsed-in-a-government-funding-bill-despite-big-support-in-congress/articleshow/104250825.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104250825.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰援助在国会的崩溃是在数月之内造成的，一小部分但直言不讳的共和党议员加大了反对向海外提供资金以对抗俄罗斯的努力。尽管华盛顿两党压倒性地支持阻止普京的入侵，但未能批准乌克兰援助对政府来说是一个挫折。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 02:32:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/how-6-billion-in-ukraine-aid-collapsed-in-a-government-funding-bill-despite-big-support-in-congress/articleshow/104250825.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日利亚呼吁缓和以色列与哈马斯之间的敌对行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigeria-calls-for-de-escalation-of-hostilities-between-israel-hamas/articleshow/104250619.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104250619.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼日利亚政府对以色列和哈马斯之间的敌对行动表示担忧，并呼吁缓和局势并停火。尼日利亚敦促双方优先考虑平民的安全，并进行对话以和平解决冲突。非洲联盟也表达了关切，并呼吁结束军事敌对行动并恢复两国建国谈判。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 02:15:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigeria-calls-for-de-escalation-of-hostilities-between-israel-hamas/articleshow/104250619.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯突然袭击以色列和地区安全调整</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/in-surprise-attack-hamas-strikes-israel-and-regional-security-realignment/articleshow/104250126.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104250126.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯最近对以色列的袭击不仅针对该国的安全，还旨在破坏可能威胁巴勒斯坦建国愿望和伊朗利益的潜在区域安全联盟。这次袭击恰逢沙特阿拉伯和以色列关系正常化的努力，这将影响沙特阿拉伯最近与伊朗的和解。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 01:06:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/in-surprise-attack-hamas-strikes-israel-and-regional-security-realignment/articleshow/104250126.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击暴露情报漏洞后，以色列安全部队面临质疑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-security-forces-face-questions-after-hamas-attack-lays-bare-intelligence-gaps/articleshow/104250002.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104250002.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列正面临着哈马斯武装分子冲破加沙周围屏障发动致命袭击的措手不及的问题。这次袭击造成大量平民死亡，被描述为一次意外事件和一次情报失误。以色列此前曾采取激励和限制相结合的措施来维持加沙的稳定，但最近的袭击暴露了其安全机构的漏洞。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 00:50:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-security-forces-face-questions-after-hamas-attack-lays-bare-intelligence-gaps/articleshow/104250002.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰总统泽伦斯基呼吁世界声援以色列</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskyy-calls-for-world-solidarity-with-israel/articleshow/104249608.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104249608.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;自 2022 年 2 月俄罗斯入侵开始以来，乌克兰与以色列的关系一直紧张。内塔尼亚胡虽然向乌克兰提供了大量人道主义援助，但始终拒绝向基辅供应武器。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 23:35:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskyy-calls-for-world-solidarity-with-israel/articleshow/104249608.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国表示正在与其他国家合作防止加沙冲突蔓延</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-says-it-is-working-with-others-to-prevent-gaza-conflict-from-spreading/articleshow/104249520.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104249520.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府一名高级官员周六表示，哈马斯在以色列发动致命袭击后，美国正在与其他国家政府合作，确保危机不会蔓延并控制在加沙。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 23:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-says-it-is-working-with-others-to-prevent-gaza-conflict-from-spreading/articleshow/104249520.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯暴力迫使沙特与以色列的势头绕道</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-violently-forces-detour-from-saudi-israel-momentum/articleshow/104249507.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104249507.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 23:06:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-violently-forces-detour-from-saudi-israel-momentum/articleshow/104249507.cms</guid></item><item><title>斯通曼·威利以詹姆斯·墨菲身份安葬 128 年后安葬</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/stoneman-willie-buried-after-128-years-as-james-murphy/articleshow/104249505.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104249505.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 《石头人威利》的故事可以追溯到1895年，当时一名假名的小偷在监狱中去世。他的尸体无人认领，被送往 Theo C. Auman 殡仪馆，在那里发生了奇怪的事件——他被殡仪馆意外制成木乃伊。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 23:02:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/stoneman-willie-buried-after-128-years-as-james-murphy/articleshow/104249505.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>